{"id":579948530,"lang":"java","time":"1 month, 3 weeks","timestamp":1635686511,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"8 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/579948530/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"40 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubstring(String s) {\n        String test = \"\";\n        \n        int maxLength = -1;\n        \n        if(s.isEmpty()){\n            return 0;\n        }else if(s.length() == 1){\n             return 1;\n        }\n        \n        for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {\n            String current = String.valueOf(c);\n \n            if (test.contains(current)) {\n                test = test.substring(test.indexOf(current) + 1);\n            }\n            test = test + String.valueOf(c);\n            maxLength = Math.max(test.length(), maxLength);\n        }\n \n        \n        return maxLength;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters"}
